<para> </para><itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="compact"><listitem>You need 3rd party ODBC drivers that connect to your database.
</listitem>
<listitem>You need to install your Single-Tier driver or Multi-Tier driver server components (Request Broker &amp; Generic ODBC Agent) on the machine, which contains the 3rd party ODBC drivers.
</listitem>
<listitem>Your client application must reside on the same machine as the Single-Tier driver or the Multi-Tier driver client components.</listitem>
